      "id": "PopularPost264480",
      "post_content": "Its that kind of card you don't want to draw early or at least not twice, but which can get surprisingly powerful when it shows up at a convenient moment.  \n  \nIt's basically a slowtrip\\* that gives you [Goblin Recruiter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Recruiter)'s effect for creatures in your graveyard.  \nIf your opponent doesn't have any means to manipulate your library (e.g. by [milling it](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=205000) or [shuffling it](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=29849)), this can be a very powerful effect.  \n  \nAlso since you can predict your next couple of draws, cards like [Polymorph](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polymorph) and [Impromptu Raid](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Impromptu Raid) can become handy.  \n  \n\\*A slowtrip is a portmonteau for a particular effect mostly seen on older cards. They work like regular cantrips (which means the spell lets you draw a card when it resolves), yet - as you can tell by taking a look at the card - have this effect delayed until the next turn.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost264480\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Its that kind of card you don't want to draw early or at least not twice, but which can get surprisingly powerful when it shows up at a convenient moment.<br/><br/>It's basically a slowtrip* that gives you <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Recruiter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Recruiter\">Goblin Recruiter</a>'s effect for creatures in your graveyard.<br/>If your opponent doesn't have any means to manipulate your library (e.g. by <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"205000\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=205000\">milling it</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"29849\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=29849\">shuffling it</a>), this can be a very powerful effect.<br/><br/>Also since you can predict your next couple of draws, cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Polymorph\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Polymorph\">Polymorph</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Impromptu Raid\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Impromptu Raid\">Impromptu Raid</a> can become handy.<br/><br/>*A slowtrip is a portmonteau for a particular effect mostly seen on older cards. They work like regular cantrips (which means the spell lets you draw a card when it resolves), yet - as you can tell by taking a look at the card - have this effect delayed until the next turn.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '264480'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (8/26/2012 5:48:13 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
